Total letters: 373
Total words: 76
Average number of letters per word (A) = 373 / 76 ≈ 4.91

Step 2: Calculate B, the percentage of words with more than 6 letters.

1. Count the number of words with more than 6 letters:
- nollstället (11 letters)
